---
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro';
---
<Layout
  title="3D Machine — Customer Story — Formic"
  description="3D Machine, a contract CNC shop in Goodland, Indiana, automated a monotonous machine-tending job with Formic Tend — adding ~2,000 production hours in half a year and 25% more capacity, with zero capital risk."
  ogTitle="3D Machine — Formic Customer Story"
  ogDescription="25% more capacity · ~2,000 production hours · zero capital"
>
  <link rel="canonical" href="https://formic.co/stories/3d-machine" slot="head" />

<div class="detail-bc">
  <a href="/">Home</a><span class="sep">/</span><a href="/stories">Customer Stories</a><span class="sep">/</span>3D Machine
</div>

<section class="detail-hero">
  <div class="si">
    <div class="slabel" style="color:var(--orange)">Customer Story · 3D Machine</div>
    <h1 style="font-size:clamp(32px,3.8vw,56px)">3D Machine Finds New Competitive Edge with Automation Partner Formic</h1>
    <p class="lede">3D Machine — a contract CNC shop in Goodland, Indiana — automated a monotonous machine-tending job with Formic Tend, adding roughly 2,000 production hours in half a year and 25% more capacity, with zero capital risk.</p>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="detail-block dark">
  <div class="detail-video wide">
    <div class="detail-video-frame">
      <img src="/stories/3d-machine-hero.jpg" alt="3D Machine CNC machine-tending automation" />
      <span class="dv-cap">3D Machine · Goodland, Indiana</span>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="detail-block white" style="padding:64px 0 0">
  <div class="si" style="max-width:1280px;margin:0 auto;padding:0 80px">
    <div class="db-tag">At a glance</div>
    <div style="display:grid;grid-template-columns:repeat(auto-fit,minmax(150px,1fr));gap:1px;background:var(--lgrey);border:1px solid var(--lgrey);margin-top:14px">
      <div style="background:var(--white);padding:18px 20px"><div style="font-family:var(--mono);font-size:9px;font-weight:500;letter-spacing:.18em;text-transform:uppercase;color:var(--mgrey);margin-bottom:6px">Founded</div><div style="font-family:var(--sans);font-size:17px;font-weight:500;letter-spacing:-.01em;color:var(--black)">1996</div></div>
      <div style="background:var(--white);padding:18px 20px"><div style="font-family:var(--mono);font-size:9px;font-weight:500;letter-spacing:.18em;text-transform:uppercase;color:var(--mgrey);margin-bottom:6px">Location</div><div style="font-family:var(--sans);font-size:17px;font-weight:500;letter-spacing:-.01em;color:var(--black)">Goodland, Indiana</div></div>
      <div style="background:var(--white);padding:18px 20px"><div style="font-family:var(--mono);font-size:9px;font-weight:500;letter-spacing:.18em;text-transform:uppercase;color:var(--mgrey);margin-bottom:6px">Industry</div><div style="font-family:var(--sans);font-size:17px;font-weight:500;letter-spacing:-.01em;color:var(--black)">Contract CNC machining</div></div>
      <div style="background:var(--white);padding:18px 20px"><div style="font-family:var(--mono);font-size:9px;font-weight:500;letter-spacing:.18em;text-transform:uppercase;color:var(--mgrey);margin-bottom:6px">Solution</div><div style="font-family:var(--sans);font-size:17px;font-weight:500;letter-spacing:-.01em;color:var(--black)">Formic Tend™</div></div>
      <div style="background:var(--white);padding:18px 20px"><div style="font-family:var(--mono);font-size:9px;font-weight:500;letter-spacing:.18em;text-transform:uppercase;color:var(--mgrey);margin-bottom:6px">Commitment</div><div style="font-family:var(--sans);font-size:17px;font-weight:500;letter-spacing:-.01em;color:var(--black)">1-year term</div></div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="detail-block white">
  <div class="db-grid">
    <div class="db-text">
      <div class="db-tag">01 — The Challenge</div>
      <h2>The job <em>nobody wanted to run</em>.</h2>
      <p>3D Machine, founded in 1996 by brothers Tim and Dave Deno, runs high-volume CNC production that required manual machine tending on a Mori Seiki lathe and a Haas CNC machine. Operators disliked the monotonous station, which hurt motivation — and as a contract manufacturer with order forecasts only about 12 months out, capital investment in automation felt too risky.</p>
      <ul class="feats">
        <li>High-volume CNC with manual machine tending</li>
        <li>Monotonous station hurting operator motivation</li>
        <li>~12-month forecasts made CapEx risky</li>
      </ul>
    </div>
    <div class="db-img"><img src="/stories/3d-machine-2.jpg" alt="Formic Tend robot tending a CNC machine" loading="lazy"/><span class="img-cap">Machine tending · automated</span></div>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="detail-block lgrey">
  <div class="db-grid flip">
    <div class="db-img"><img src="/MachineTending-CNC.jpg" alt="Fanuc robot automating CNC machine tending" loading="lazy"/><span class="img-cap">Formic Tend · Fanuc M-10iD</span></div>
    <div class="db-text">
      <div class="db-tag">02 — The Solution</div>
      <h2>Click "run", <em>and walk away</em>.</h2>
      <p>3D Machine deployed Formic Tend with zero capital investment, an hourly usage rate, and a one-year commitment. A Fanuc M-10iD robot automates the six-step process — loading aluminum rings through the lathe, shear, CNC milling, and output. Performance guarantees, a dedicated success team, 24/7 monitoring, lifetime maintenance, and equipment repurposing are all bundled into the flat hourly rate.</p>
      <ul class="feats">
        <li>Formic Tend: $0 capital, hourly rate, 1-year term</li>
        <li>Fanuc M-10iD automates the full six-step cycle</li>
        <li>Monitoring, maintenance, and repurposing included</li>
      </ul>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="detail-block white" style="padding:88px 80px">
  <div class="si" style="max-width:900px;margin:0 auto;padding:0">
    <div class="pull-quote">
      <blockquote>"What's great is that our team can now set up the system, click 'run', and walk away. Not only can we use those people for other jobs, but we're getting an extra batch of production at the end of the day."</blockquote>
      <cite>Tim Deno · Co-Founder & President, 3D Machine</cite>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="detail-block dark">
  <div class="si" style="max-width:1280px;margin:0 auto;padding:80px;text-align:center">
    <div class="db-tag" style="justify-content:center">03 — The Results</div>
    <h2 style="font-family:var(--sans);font-size:clamp(40px,5vw,72px);font-weight:500;letter-spacing:-.02em;line-height:1;color:var(--white);margin:18px 0 56px">A real <em style="color:var(--orange);font-style:normal">competitive edge.</em></h2>
    <div style="display:grid;grid-template-columns:repeat(3,1fr);gap:1px;background:rgba(255,255,255,.1)">
      <div style="background:var(--black);padding:36px 24px"><div style="font-family:var(--sans);font-size:48px;font-weight:500;color:var(--orange);line-height:1">25%</div><div style="font-family:var(--mono);font-size:10px;letter-spacing:.18em;text-transform:uppercase;color:rgba(240,245,241,.55);margin-top:12px">More production capacity</div></div>
      <div style="background:var(--black);padding:36px 24px"><div style="font-family:var(--sans);font-size:48px;font-weight:500;color:var(--orange);line-height:1">~2,000</div><div style="font-family:var(--mono);font-size:10px;letter-spacing:.18em;text-transform:uppercase;color:rgba(240,245,241,.55);margin-top:12px">Production hours, H1 2023</div></div>
      <div style="background:var(--black);padding:36px 24px"><div style="font-family:var(--sans);font-size:48px;font-weight:500;color:var(--orange);line-height:1">$0</div><div style="font-family:var(--mono);font-size:10px;letter-spacing:.18em;text-transform:uppercase;color:rgba(240,245,241,.55);margin-top:12px">Capital invested</div></div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="detail-cta">
  <h2>Find your <em>competitive edge</em>.</h2>
  <div class="btn-row">
    <a href="mailto:sales@formic.co" class="btn-ctadark">Get Started</a>
    <a href="/stories" class="btn-ctawh">More Customer Stories</a>
  </div>
</section>
</Layout>
